{"TopicId":187338,"ForumId":109,"TopicTitle":"KSP2 Hype Train Thread","CreatedByName":"Whirligig Girl","CreatedById":36077,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T20:46:45Z","PageNum":208,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Stoup","CreatedById":2804,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-21T22:01:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat definitely gets my curiosity, and it\u0027ll make a nice first plane destination!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWas it Matt Lowne that had to censor some of his footage due to a bugged out interaction with a spoiler asset on his way to Duna? Maybe it\u0027s something similar\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-21T22:02:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224236774\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677016863\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u00222804\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stoup\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Stoup said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nspoiler asset on his way to Duna? Maybe it\u0027s something similar\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think that was the\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nface on Duna\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Strawberry","CreatedById":222150,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-21T22:03:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224236774\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677016863\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u00222804\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stoup\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Stoup said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat definitely gets my curiosity, and it\u0027ll make a nice first plane destination!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWas it Matt Lowne that had to censor some of his footage due to a bugged out interaction with a spoiler asset on his way to Duna? Maybe it\u0027s something similar\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nObsidian ant, I doubt its related as the rock that was chasing them happened when they entered dunas \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003Esoi\u003C/abbr\u003E and the rock was red, so it probably was a duna asset that went rogue.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stoup","CreatedById":2804,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-21T22:06:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, I didn\u0027t necessarily mean the exact some one, but maybe a case of one misplaced asset, two misplaced asset \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-21T22:08:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy is it still 21st here\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-02-21T22:08:21Z\u0022 title=\u002202/21/2023 10:08  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 21, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by The Aziz\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-21T22:34:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd another thing.. Scott Manley mentioned\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsearching for the Mohole but said it was moved..\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd also he tweeted that\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthe kraken lives on.. so maybe he\u0027s talking about the dead one on ...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-21T23:06:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is 22th, means it\u0027s only 63 hours left\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Minmus Taster","CreatedById":206159,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-21T23:49:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nT-3\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMain engine startup\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Astr0Guy5","CreatedById":225367,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-21T23:54:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe closer it gets, the more surreal it feels.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3 days after 3 years\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DwightLee","CreatedById":199897,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-22T00:16:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224236843\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677023665\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022225367\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Astr0Guy5\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 minutes ago, Astr0Guy5 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe closer it gets, the more surreal it feels.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3 days after 3 years\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, one thing I always lamented about KSP is that I was not there from the beginning. I wont miss out on that chance this time.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know early access is not for everyone, but for me I will enjoy giving feedback, and being there for the ride from day one enjoying every patch, every major update, and hopefully years in the future for future DLC of KSP 2\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JoeSchmuckatelli","CreatedById":154477,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-22T00:24:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224236843\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677023665\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022225367\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Astr0Guy5\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n28 minutes ago, Astr0Guy5 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe closer it gets, the more surreal it feels.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3 days after 3 years\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI keep checking...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...but it\u0027s still not Friday, yet\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Astr0Guy5","CreatedById":225367,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-22T00:46:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224236851\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677025019\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199897\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DwightLee\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n23 minutes ago, DwightLee said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, one thing I always lamented about KSP is that I was not there from the beginning. I wont miss out on that chance this time.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know early access is not for everyone, but for me I will enjoy giving feedback, and being there for the ride from day one enjoying every patch, every major update, and hopefully years in the future for future DLC of KSP 2\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSame. I\u0027m still crossing my fingers my PC can run KSP2, though, so I might not be there for the entire journey.\u00A0 You can bet I\u0027ll be there in spirit though!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"t_v","CreatedById":213541,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-22T00:51:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224236742\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677014710\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022219348\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vl3d\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Vl3d said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh.. nothing..\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EReveal hidden contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.ibb.co/1JJXr99/KSP2-Anomaly-2.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022KSP2-Anomaly-2.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002241.56\u0022 height=\u0022266\u0022 width=\u0022640\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.ibb.co/1JJXr99/KSP2-Anomaly-2.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNothing at all...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EReveal hidden contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.ibb.co/sQWyDMz/KSP2-Anomaly-3.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022KSP2-Anomaly-3.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022135.21\u0022 height=\u0022937\u0022 width=\u0022693\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.ibb.co/sQWyDMz/KSP2-Anomaly-3.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.ibb.co/YbtM98V/KSP2-Anomaly-1-2.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022KSP2-Anomaly-1-2.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002271.00\u0022 height=\u0022753\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.ibb.co/YbtM98V/KSP2-Anomaly-1-2.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA purple, yellow and green nothing!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe two explanations I see being more likely than most are that 1) it is intentional, there are structures of some sort that are shining lights, or 2) it is unintentional, and something about rendering that location (which might have structures) is causing those flashes (because we haven\u2019t seen them in any other location)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-22T00:55:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy countdown clock says 2. Which it will be after I sleep. Guess it\u0027s a good idea.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheOtherDave","CreatedById":32305,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-22T03:31:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224236851\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677025019\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199897\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DwightLee\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, DwightLee said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, one thing I always lamented about KSP is that I was not there from the beginning. I wont miss out on that chance this time.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know early access is not for everyone, but for me I will enjoy giving feedback, and being there for the ride from day one enjoying every patch, every major update, and hopefully years in the future for future DLC of KSP 2\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEarly access would \u003Cem\u003Etotally\u003C/em\u003E be for me, if only it had macOS support.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"magnemoe","CreatedById":57801,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-22T04:01:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224236718\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677012956\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022219348\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vl3d\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 hours ago, Vl3d said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou guys are gonna love this!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.ibb.co/mBj61HJ/KSP2-Anomaly-1.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022KSP2-Anomaly-1.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002298.42\u0022 height=\u0022659\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.ibb.co/mBj61HJ/KSP2-Anomaly-1.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooking at the huge telescope with the spheres behind, is I the only one wanting to fill it with hydrogen tanks\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nEdit: did not see the weird light, weird none flew over to it. my guess its an structure like an lighthouse.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-02-22T11:42:22Z\u0022 title=\u002202/22/2023 11:42  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 22, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by magnemoe\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GoldForest","CreatedById":77770,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-22T05:43:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224236869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677027319\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy countdown clock says 2. Which it will be after I sleep. Guess it\u0027s a good idea.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n56 hours, 18 minutes and 50 second as of right now.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-22T11:17:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy message is very clear. I personally do not care about anything else but having KSP2 be the best game ever made.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t care about any arguments or hesitations. I don\u0027t care about your video card or your color preferences or what parts you want. I don\u0027t care about words anymore.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis Friday is the moment \u003Cstrong\u003Eyou\u003C/strong\u003E \u003Cstrong\u003Ehave to do your duty\u003C/strong\u003E. For technology. For science. For space exploration. For the community.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSupport KSP and buy the game!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo ifs, buts or maybes. Just buy the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EBUY THE GAME!\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-02-22T11:25:22Z\u0022 title=\u002202/22/2023 11:25  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 22, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Vl3d\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"K^2","CreatedById":57710,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-22T11:33:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have no idea if this is a parody, but I love it anyways.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t think early access is for everyone. I do think a lot of people will be disappointed, at least in the short term, if they buy it right now without thinking. But at the same time, a lot of people will get this early access and enjoy playing through it, and watching how the game develops from here. And the fact that some people want to present getting into the early access as an\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Eunreasonable\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0option is absolutely ridiculous. So I\u0027m completely on board with the energy of this, \u0022Don\u0027t care, getting the game,\u0022 thread.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn a more serious note, one group of people who should be getting this and other games in early, unfinished state, though, is anyone studying game development. The two best ways to learn from games made by professionals without working for a studio is working on mods or playing games that aren\u0027t finished. Just like it\u0027s a lot easier to read the intentions of a level designer on a blocked out map, before all the decoration went in, so it is with understanding the game mechanics and even aspects of code performance and complexity while you\u0027re playing something with some inner parts of the game exposed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"modus","CreatedById":207631,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-22T12:12:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224237124\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022212195\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677064627\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022219348\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vl3d\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n52 minutes ago, Vl3d said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy message is very clear. I personally do not care about anything else but having KSP2 be the best game ever made.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t care about any arguments or hesitations. I don\u0027t care about your video card or your color preferences or what parts you want. I don\u0027t care about words anymore.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis Friday is the moment \u003Cstrong\u003Eyou\u003C/strong\u003E \u003Cstrong\u003Ehave to do your duty\u003C/strong\u003E. For technology. For science. For space exploration. For the community.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSupport KSP and buy the game!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo ifs, buts or maybes. Just buy the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EBUY THE GAME!\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo you\u0027re saying I should..buy the game, is that correct?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue2.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m totally gonna buy it\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tstein","CreatedById":223854,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-22T12:16:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell I wil NOT buy it at this moment because my computer cannot handle it and\u00A0\u00A0 here in Brazil where I am living a computer that can run it\u00A0 cost as much as 4 months of a Senior AI engineer (not to forget that hassle of upgrading and changing all your stuff into a new machine when your computer is not just a video game, but a work tool ).... so pass for now considering\u00A0 my current computer runs all other games that I\u00A0 like to play very well.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-02-22T12:28:51Z\u0022 title=\u002202/22/2023 12:28  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 22, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by tstein\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pandaman","CreatedById":130621,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-22T12:26:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith respect\u00A0 to \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/219348-vl3d/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022219348\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/219348-vl3d/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Vl3d\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0that statement\u00A0 came across a bit too \u0027evangelical\u0027 for my tastes...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHowever, personally I intend\u00A0 to buy it anyway take my chances.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have serious doubts that my graphics card will suffice, but only one way to find out...\u00A0 I planned on upgrading before too long (fairly old PC), but I may need to look at doing it sooner than I hoped.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EWorst\u00A0 case scenario\u00A0 have the game at a discount over final\u00A0 v1.0 release\u00A0 price.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NutellaSandwich","CreatedById":207876,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-22T12:58:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2 DAYS!!!! WOOO!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-22T13:10:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo, I won\u0027t.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe publisher\u0027s decision to make the purchase legally\u00A0impossible in my country totally matches my decision to postpone this at least till the next technological epoch.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThus we are united in our efforts \u003Cem\u003E[snip]\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll I needed was a more stable KSP-1, not 45 GB for an early KSP-1 clone, when the developed KSP-1 occupies just 6 (ok, 10 together with mods).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-02-22T19:14:43Z\u0022 title=\u002202/22/2023 07:14  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 22, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Starhawk\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003ERedacted by moderator\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-22T13:12:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMerged with the hype train thread.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}